             was indicted for <rs id="t18030525-28-off155" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030525-28-off155" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030525-28-off155" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030525-28-cd156" type="crimeDate">7th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030525-28-off155 t18030525-28-cd156"></join>, two sheets, value 4s. a counterpane, value 8s. and a tablecloth, value 2s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18030525-28-victim238" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Lewis
                     <interp inst="t18030525-28-victim238" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
