                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030525-28-defend237 t18030525-28-punish160"></join>
               Confined one month in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Grose.</p>
